name: Alchemist-mix
description:
这是一个混合生成的模型，在高清晰重绘的状态下长生成晶莹剔透的角色。推荐：R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6B。

粗线条导致在大多数情况下手脚比较稳定，但可能会有人不是很喜欢这种画风。

不适合合成高大威猛的角色，在低分率下表现出极差。

预览图使用的TAG是不完整的，需要添加一些你我都懂的TAG。

“初极狭……”——晋·陶渊明

“这个P怎么露小缝啊？”——SCboy

吐司链接https://tusi.art/models/605031433104440721

This is a hybrid generative model grown into a crystal clear character in a state of high definition repaint. Recommended: R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6B

Thick lines lead to more stable hands and feet in most cases, but some people may not like this style of painting.

It is not suitable for synthesizing tall and powerful characters, and the performance is extremely poor at low score rates.

The TAG used in the preview image is incomplete, and some TAGs that both you and I understand need to be added.

"The beginning is very narrow..." ——Jin·Tao Yuanming

"Why does this P show a small gap?"——SCboy
